  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Black Friday 2024 | Inghams Ski, Walking and Lapland holidays</h2>
<ul>
<li>Save an extra £100 per booking when you book a Ski, Walking or Lapland holiday​.</li>
<li>Valid on holidays departing in Winter 2024/25, 2025/26 and Summer 2025​.</li>
<li>Applicable on all destinations and departure dates​.</li>
<li>Only valid on packages, which include your travel from the UK, transfers and accommodation​.</li>
<li>The discount will have automatically applied to you booking and the prices you see on the website will already in the saving.​</li>
<li>This offer can be used at the same time as other Inghams offers in market.​</li>
<li>This offer is available from Thursday 21 November until Monday 2 December at 23:59​.</li>
<li>This offer can be booked online or via our call centre.​</li>
<li>This offer is available to new bookings only.​</li>
<li>Offer is subject to availability and we reserve the right to amend or withdraw this offer at any time, without notice.</li>
</ul>
